snippet.title: Hero in the Castle of Doom [Arcade Longplay] (1984) Seatongrove UK, Ltd. {Donkey Kong conversion}
snippet.description: Full playthrough of the arcade game Hero in the Castle of Doom. Donkey Kong conversion by Seatongrove UK, Ltd. Released back in 1984. Similar to the game Hero. but with different graphics.
